---
title: Tex-Mex Beef & Pepper Enchiladas with Pico de Gallo & Lime Crema
description: When it comes to Mexican food, burritos typically get all the glory. In our humble opinion, enchiladas are a total unsung dinner hero. Technically easier-to-assemble burritos smothered in a delicious sauce, these weeknight wonders offer so much more than “food on the table.” This Tex-Mex version is filled with a combo of spiced beef and green pepper, topped with a bold red sauce and Mexican cheese, then baked until bubbly and melty. With a finishing touch of fresh pico and lime crema, that’s a whole ‘lada deliciousness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6407525e89a1be4fa5047ed6-cb87a18b.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/6488824b8b1fa4d79c4450d1.pdf
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/tex-mex-beef-and-pepper-enchiladas-6488824b8b1fa4d79c4450d1
course: main course
author: Michelle Doll Olson
time required: 40 minutes
cuisine: Mexican
